      Parameters:
      questionContent - - String containing the question content
      approved - - boolean status for if a question is approved to be visible to all
      reviewed - - boolean status for if a question has been reviewed by a trainer or sales
      categoryTag - - An enum value that corresponds to the category of the question
      formatTag - - An enum value that corresponds to the format of the question
      contentTypeTag - - An enum value that corresponds to the content type of the question
      user - - The user that owns/created the question
